<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.3">
<l>taṭampaṭu tāmaraip poykai kalakki</l>
<l>viṭampaṭu nākattai vālpaṟṟi yīrttu</l>
<l>paṭampaṭu paintalai mēleḻap pāyntiṭṭu</l>
<l>uṭampaiya caittāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">ucciyil niṉṟāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having agitated the broad lotus pond.</l>
<l>Grasping and pulling at the tail of the venemous snake,</l>
<l>He lept up atop [it’s] head with hoods spread.</l>
<l>Because of he who moved [his] body,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end</l>
<l>Because of he who stood atop [the snake’s] head,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
